{"id":597058,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/狸片-碧桂园降价触发暴力维权/","date":"2018-10-06T17:15:26Z","modified":"2018-10-06T17:16:45Z","title":"狸片 | 碧桂园降价触发暴力维权","content":"<p><br class=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597059\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/6-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/6-4.jpg 547w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/6-4-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597060\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/7-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/7-4.jpg 494w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/7-4-300x172.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>10月4日，上饶碧桂园信州府因价格从10000降到7000，被大量业主维权，导致售楼部被“真刀真枪”打砸，成为2018年中国楼市真正意义上的“第一砸”！</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597061\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/8-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"651\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/8-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/8-3-230x300.jpg 230w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/8-3-768x1001.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/8-3-786x1024.jpg 786w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597063\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/9-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"638\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/9-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/9-3-235x300.jpg 235w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/9-3-768x981.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/9-3-802x1024.jpg 802w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>有消息称，该项目之前售卖1万是精装房，现在7000是毛坯价。</p>\n<p>市场下行之际 ，降价在所难免。</p>\n<p>9月初，恒大在全国发起89折优惠，抢先出货回笼现金的意图已经非常明显。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597064\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/10-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"891\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/10-2.jpg 847w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/10-2-168x300.jpg 168w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/10-2-768x1369.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/10-2-574x1024.jpg 574w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>不过，降价最早引发退房的却是碧桂园。</p>\n<p>近日，上海浦东桂园南郡项目出现大规模业主退房事件，因阴阳合同不按上海市政府要求的一房一价政策进行销售。</p>\n<p>这次碧桂园的阴阳合同，则是以阳合同维持一个表面高价，暗地里以阴合同低于政府规定的价格进行销售，一夜之间将备案均价从35000直接降到28000至26000进行销售。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597065\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/11-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"524\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/11-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/11-3-286x300.jpg 286w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/11-3-768x804.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/11-3-978x1024.jpg 978w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>楼盘打折销售，业主躁动维权，是中国楼市的特色。</p>\n<p>2018，万科在杭州楼盘因75折促销，售楼处被砸。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597066\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/12-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"238\" /></p>\n<p>如今长沙楼市大热的天健城，2008年也曾因降价，售楼部被业主砸坏。</p>\n<p>转载来源网络，若与版权冲突请联系删除</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p>相关阅读：</p></blockquote>\n<ul class=\"st-related-posts\">\n<li>\n<blockquote><p><span class=\"related_date\">2018.08.16</span> <a title=\"兽爷：不管是天猫还是死猫，能圈到钱就是好猫？\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%e5%85%bd%e7%88%b7%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8d%e7%ae%a1%e6%98%af%e5%a4%a9%e7%8c%ab%e8%bf%98%e6%98%af%e6%ad%bb%e7%8c%ab%ef%bc%8c%e8%83%bd%e5%9c%88%e5%88%b0%e9%92%b1%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e5%a5%